headline: Otis Worldwide's Quarterly Earnings Preview: What You Need to Know
summary: Otis Worldwide is scheduled to release its fiscal fourth-quarter earnings later this month, and analysts project a high single-digit earnings growth.

headline: Otis Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Earnings Advisory
summary: Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: OTIS) will host a conference call on Wednesday, January 28, 2026, at 8:30 a.m. ET. Otis Chair, CEO & President Judy Marks and Executive Vice President & CFO Cristina Mendez will discuss the company's fourth quarter and full year results and 2026 outlook.
